,h$, where $h$ is the entropy of the associated Markov\nprobability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Aug 2019 23:14:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 12:21:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Sep 2021 02:16:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-16"}
